lings on the Yukawa-induced\ndynamically-generated masses. For the case where the fermions are right-handed\nneutrinos, we compare such masses with the radiative ones induced by both, the\nanti-Hermitian anomalous terms and the anti-Hermitian Yukawa interactions in\nphenomenologically relevant models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2020 17:31:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-15"}
