y test results, and lessons learned from GBS20v0 and the\ndesign of GBS20v1 which will be not only a test chip but also a user chip with\n16 input data channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 04:24:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-02"}
