 results from fault-injection and neutron\nirradiation tests at the TRIGA reactor of the Jozef Stefan Institute\n(Ljubljana, Slovenia) and we compare the performance of our solution to the\nXilinx Soft Error Mitigation controller.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 11:13:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
