f order $q$. These examples can be\nlifted to non-elementary abelian groups using $p$-adic techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 15:56:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 09:47:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
